{"tid":2347951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"追蹤契媽｜Cathie Wood撈中概股 5日掃1億美金騰訊ADR","createTime":"2020-12-31T11:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T12:36:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d0db43ff5ad2b9d6ca77bb60fe59f91f31406885","tid":2347951,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"阿里巴巴（9988）受中國政府全面整治之下，美股（BABA）被拋售，曾於12月24日平安夜大跌17.6%，年內至今股價升幅收窄至12.4%，同時拖累一眾美股上市的中概股。<br />\n<br />\n不過低殘價股引起女股神Cathie Wood注意，系內ARKW及ARKF自24日起計合共買入99,448股BABA，其間BABA股價由最低211.23美元反彈至周三收238.39美元，反彈幅度接近近13%，以30日收市價計算價值2370萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n彭博數據顯示，ARK系內ETF資產總值約358億美元，其實BABA持倉價值僅僅1.3億美元，僅佔ARK系列ETF倉位0.36%。<br />\n<br />\n反而跟隨阿里下挫的騰訊ADR對Cathie Wood來說更吸引，系內4隻ETF均在24日起合共掃入140萬股騰訊ADR，現價總值1億美元。<br />\n<br />\n然而眾多中概股入面，最受Cathie Wood注視的其實是百度（BIDU）。其中的原因相信是百度傳出計劃生產電動車，女股神旗艦ARKK在12月其間掃入106萬股BIDU，月內股價飆升58%，單計ARKK手上BIDU市值達2.3億美元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201231/FEC2VZGOFJHBZNBVPE4QGN5Z6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201231%2FFEC2VZGOFJHBZNBVPE4QGN5Z6Y%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=d22e2691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201231%2FFEC2VZGOFJHBZNBVPE4QGN5Z6Y%2F&h=a935a209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201231/FEC2VZGOFJHBZNBVPE4QGN5Z6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"e46f055cda14fe28f09fad07a9039445b4bb8186","tid":2347951,"uid":336590,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710eacfb71ab2314232a5f60937cffc2d6e84f8b","tid":2347951,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOPfaNW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOPfaNW.png&h=84482ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br /